      "role": "user",
      "content": "understood. what if the encroachment is small but persistent, like an unrecorded extension or some sort of structural overlap that isn't easily visible from the street? how does the city typically handle those kinds of \"hidden\" boundary issues during inspections, and is there a way to resolve them before they turn into a full-blown legal dispute?",
